    <articleReference>
      <Value><![CDATA[Laboratory of Pharmacology and Experimental Therapeutics, Department of Pharmacology, Institute of Biomedical Sciences, University of São Paulo (USP), Av. Prof. Lineu Prestes, 1524, Butantan, São Paulo, SP, 05508-900, Brazil.]]></Value>
    </articleReference>
    <articleTitle>
      <Value><![CDATA[Effects of photobiomodulation therapy, pharmacological therapy, and physical exercise as single and/or combined treatment on the inflammatory response induced by experimental osteoarthritis]]></Value>
    </articleTitle>
